<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1911-02-08T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1911-02-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="1018" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1018">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 816.032.</note>
                        <head>[Untitled]</head>
                        <p rend="center">[Translation of extract concerning the United States.]</p>
                        <p>I have given particular attention to increasing the cordiality o: our
                            relations with the United States of America, whose altruistic spirit
                            toward the other nations of this continent I take pleasure in
                            recognizing and proclaiming. * * *</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Fernando Figueroa.</hi></signed>
                            <lb/>
                            <dateline rendition="#left"><date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-02-08">February 8, 1911</date>.</dateline>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                </body></text></TEI>